  <description type="morphology">Plants 25–60 cm. Stems yellowish green, often leafless at flowering, densely,
        compactly tomentose. Leaves yellowish green; blades 1-nerved, filiform, 10–30 × 0.8–1 mm,
        faces glabrate. Involucres 8–11.5 mm. Phyllaries 17–31, apices erect, acute to obtuse,
        abaxial faces glabrous. Corollas 5–8.5 mm, tubes mostly glabrous, lobes 0.5–1.1 mm (erect to
        incurved), glabrous; style appendages longer than stigmatic portions. Cypselae glabrous;
        pappi 3–6.6 mm. 2n = 18.</description>
